        </item>
        <item>
            <title>GPT-4.5 測試版通知 Android 現身，僅限 Pro 用户、目前未實際推出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/chatgpt-4-5-in-android/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chatgpt-4-5-in-android</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/chatgpt-4-5-in-android/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 12:41:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-4]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-4.5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GPT-4o]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294355</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>OpenAI 即將推出 GPT-4.5，其測試版已悄然現身 Android 系統的 ChatGPT 應用程式。這款新模型將率先惠及 Pro 訂閲用户，功能可望更勝一籌，惟有 X 用户反映指目前 GPT-4.5 僅在通知出現，點擊相關通知後亦無法使用 GPT-4.5。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p dir="ltr" lang="en">I just got this on the android app! I think it&#8217;s a big but 4.5 seems imminent <a href="https://t.co/pdzCAk5IKT">pic.twitter.com/pdzCAk5IKT</a></p><p>— Dylan Neve (@DylanNeve10) <a href="https://twitter.com/DylanNeve10/status/1894685259104461249?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 26, 2025</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>有用家回報，Android 版可見試用 GPT-4.5 的通知。這款新模型預計取代免費版 ChatGPT 現行的 GPT-4o，對話容量將顯著提升，惟目前功能尚未開放，通知僅作預告，點擊後尚無回應。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294356" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ec12569ea5be8e1-694x379.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="379" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ec12569ea5be8e1-694x379.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ec12569ea5be8e1.jpeg 844w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1481874.htm">cnBeta</a></p><p>網上消息透露，OpenAI 正同步精進其網頁界面。Deep Research、Canvas 及圖像上傳等功能經重新整合，讓用户在模型間切換更得心應手。Deep Research 模式新增輸入選項，用户可上傳資料與文件，獲取深入報告。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294357" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfnawx0aaqhhs-694x376.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfnawx0aaqhhs-694x376.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfnawx0aaqhhs-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/btibor91/status/1894684174495461537">btibor91@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294358" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfnb2ayaagiwl-694x293.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="293" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfnb2ayaagiwl-694x293.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfnb2ayaagiwl-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/btibor91/status/1894684174495461537">btibor91@X</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294359" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfns1xkaajb6p-694x270.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="270" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfns1xkaajb6p-694x270.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/gktfns1xkaajb6p-scaled.jpeg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://x.com/btibor91/status/1894684174495461537">btibor91@X</a></p><p>AI 市場波瀾壯闊，OpenAI 早前推出的 o3-mini 以低成本與高推理能力脱穎而出，雖未及 o1 的頂尖水準，卻性價比出眾。然而對手來勢洶洶。DeepSeek R1 以僅 500 萬美元（約港幣 3,887 萬元）的訓練成本實現媲美 o1 的效能，震驚業界。Google 亦不甘後人，其 Gemini Flash Thinking 模型已投入戰場。Anthropic 本週亦發布 Claude 3.7 Sonnet，搭配新工具 Claude Code，搶灘市場。</p><p>GPT-4.5 的推出僅是 OpenAI 大計一環，業界揣測其終極目標或指向傳聞中的 GPT-5。新模型料將融合 o 系列優勢，進一步簡化操作體驗。惟強敵環伺，OpenAI 能否穩坐江山，尚待技術突破與市場驗證。後續焦點將落在 GPT-4.5 的實測表現。</p><p>資料來源：<span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3"><a href="https://x.com/DylanNeve10/status/1894685259104461249">DylanNeve10@X</a>、</span><a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1481874.htm">cnBeta</a><span class="css-1jxf684 r-bcqeeo r-1ttztb7 r-qvutc0 r-poiln3">、<a href="https://www.techzine.eu/news/applications/129093/gpt-4-5-release-for-chatgpt-appears-imminent/">Techzine</a></span></p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
