        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Sony 發表 2 支 G 系新鏡頭，400-800mm F6.3-8 + 16mm F1.8</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/sony-400-800mm-f638-16mm-f18/dc/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=sony-400-800mm-f638-16mm-f18</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/sony-400-800mm-f638-16mm-f18/dc/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 27 Feb 2025 10:51:34 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[數碼相機]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[相機配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[16mm F1.8]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[400-800mm F6.3-8]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294476</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 近日推出兩款全新 G 系列 E-Mount 鏡頭，分別為 FE 400-800mm F6.3-8 G OSS 超遠攝變焦鏡頭及 FE 16mm F1.8 G 超廣角定焦鏡頭。這兩款鏡頭分別針對遠攝及廣角拍攝需求，適用於拍攝野生動物、運動、風景及影片製作。</p><h2>FE 400-800mm F6.3-8 G OSS：遠距拍攝適用</h2><p>Sony FE 400-800mm F6.3-8 G OSS（SEL400800G） 為 G 系列 E-Mount 超遠攝變焦鏡頭，焦距範圍涵蓋 400mm 至 800mm，並可搭配 1.4 倍及 2 倍增距鏡，將焦距延伸至 1600mm。該鏡頭適合拍攝鳥類、野生動物、運動賽事及航空攝影。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294490" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image003-694x343.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="343" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image003-694x343.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image003.jpg 964w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294516" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294517" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-1-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294491" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image004-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image004-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image004.jpg 745w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294492" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005.jpg 740w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294493" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006.jpg 738w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294494" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007.jpg 731w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>鏡頭採用內變焦設計，變焦過程中長度保持不變，減少重心轉移對構圖穩定性的影響。光學結構包含，六片超低色散（ED）鏡片，用於減少色差，並在逆光環境下降低眩光與重影。11 片圓形光圈葉片，可提供柔和散景。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008.jpg 742w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>對焦系統方面，鏡頭配備，兩組線性馬達對焦模組，可支援快速自動對焦及精準追蹤。該鏡頭可與 Alpha 9 III 搭配使用，支援 120 fps 連拍。此外內置 Optical SteadyShot 光學防震，可減少手持拍攝時的震動，並可與具備影像穩定功能的 Alpha 機身結合使用，以提升穩定性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-4-421x580.jpg" alt="" width="421" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-4-421x580.jpg 421w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-4-scaled.jpg 653w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 421px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-5-421x580.jpg" alt="" width="421" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-5-421x580.jpg 421w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel400800g_productsh-5-scaled.jpg 653w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 421px" /></p><p>鏡頭具備防塵防潮設計，前鏡片採用氟塗層，以提升耐用性及清潔便利性。此外，三腳架安裝腳可旋轉，提供橫向及縱向構圖支援。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009.jpg 736w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 115px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;" colspan="2">發售資訊</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">售價</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">港幣 19,990 元</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">公開發售日期</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">2025 年 3 月 13 日</td></tr><tr style=