/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-4-694x567.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="567" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-4-694x567.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-4-scaled.jpg 1102w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294514" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-6-675x580.jpg" alt="" width="675" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-6-675x580.jpg 675w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/sel16f18g_productsho-6-scaled.jpg 1047w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 675px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image005-1.jpg 707w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294501" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image006-1.jpg 699w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image007-1.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="460" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294503" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image008-1.jpg" alt="" width="691" height="461" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image009-1.jpg 709w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image010-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image010-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image010-1.jpg 713w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>鏡頭內設兩片進階非球面（AA）鏡片及三片 ED 鏡片，用於減少色差與變形，提升影像解析度。最近對焦距離 0.15 米（自動對焦模式），手動對焦時可達 0.13 米，適用於特寫拍攝。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image011.jpg" alt="" width="633" height="356" /></p><p>鏡頭搭載 XD 線性馬達，提供快速自動對焦及追蹤能力。專為 XD 馬達開發的控制演算法可提升反應速度，降低震動與延遲。此外鏡頭支援 Alpha 相機內置的呼吸補償功能，以減少對焦時的畫面變化。鏡頭體積為 73.8 x 75 毫米，重量 304 克，設計輕巧便攜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/image012.jpg" alt="" width="632" height="355" /></p><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; height: 115px;"><tbody><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;" colspan="2">發售資訊</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">售價</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">港幣 6,490 元</td></tr><tr style="height: 23px;"><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">公開發售日期</td><td style="width: 50%; height: 23px;">2025 年 3 月 26 日</td></tr>