                <![CDATA[<p>智能家居安全品牌 Arlo Technologies 欣然宣佈將對旗下特定產品的建議零售價進行調整，震撼降價低至 6 折。新價格即日起生效，讓消費者能以更優惠的價格體驗 Arlo 屢獲殊榮的監控技術，並提升家居及企業安全。客户現可藉此顯著的優惠獲得業界領先的安全保障與安心體驗，包括 4K 超高清畫質、雙向語音、夜視及 AI 驅動的智能偵測等先進功能。</p><p>是次建議零售價的調整將適用於以下的重點產品（以港幣計算）：</p><table style="font-weight: 400;"><tbody><tr><td width="276"><strong>產品</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>原價</strong></p><p><strong>(</strong><strong>建議零售價</strong><strong>)</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>新價格</strong></p><p><strong>(</strong><strong>建議零售價</strong><strong>)</strong></td><td colspan="2" width="122"><strong>折扣</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Essential 2 </strong><strong>户外攝影機</strong><strong> – </strong><strong>單鏡裝</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$788</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$688</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$100</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>13%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Essential 2 </strong><strong>户外攝影機</strong><strong> – </strong><strong>雙鏡裝</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$1,488</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$1,288</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$200</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>13%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Pro 5S </strong><strong>無線安全攝影機 </strong><strong>– </strong><strong>單鏡裝</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$1,680</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$988</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$692</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>41%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Pro 5S </strong><strong>無線安全攝影機 </strong><strong>– </strong><strong>雙鏡裝</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$2,980</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$1,</strong><strong>8</strong><strong>88</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$1,</strong><strong>0</strong><strong>92</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>36</strong><strong>%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Ultra 2 </strong><strong>無線安全攝影機 – 單鏡裝</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$1,958</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$1,488</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$470</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>24%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Ultra 2 </strong><strong>無線安全攝影機 – 雙鏡裝</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$4,288</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$3,188</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$1,100</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>26%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Essential 2 </strong><strong>室內攝影機</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$688</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$388</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$300</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>44%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo Essential 2 </strong><strong>無線視訊門鈴</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$1,088</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$888</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$200</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>18%</strong></td></tr><tr><td width="276"><strong>Arlo </strong><strong>基站，配件</strong></td><td width="99"><strong>$788</strong></td><td width="105"><strong>$</strong><strong>63</strong><strong>8</strong></td><td width="69"><strong>$</strong><strong>15</strong><strong>0</strong></td><td width="54"><strong>19</strong><strong>%</strong></td></tr></tbody></table><h2></h2><h2><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1294484" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/02_arlopricedroppop-410x580.jpg" alt="" width="600" height="849" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/02_arlopricedroppop-410x580.jpg 410w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/02_arlopricedroppop.jpg 595w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 600px" /></h2><h2>精選優惠產品詳情</h2><h2>Arlo Ultra 2 4K UHD 無線安全攝影機</h2><p>Arlo Ultra 2 具備 HDR 技術及 4K 超高清像素，並配備 180°超廣闊對角視野和彩色夜視功能，不但能夠拍攝到更廣闊的範圍捕捉更多細節，亦能在黑夜和白晝中拍下超高清影片。最多 6 個月持久電力的超大容量電池配合 IP65 防風雨設計，確保任何時候都能為你的家庭把關。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294480" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/03_arloultra2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/03_arloultra2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/03_arloultra2-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>Arlo Pro 5S 2K 無線安全攝影機</h2><p>Arlo Pro 5S 支援雙頻 Wi-Fi，可連接 2.4 GHz 和 5 GHz 兩個頻段，令鏡頭安裝比以往更加容易，同時亦能更快更穩定地進行網絡連接，加強保障你的家居安全。 Arlo Pro 5S 2K 的電池續航力顯著提升，比 Arlo Pro 4 安全攝影機延長達 30%，配合 IP65 防風雨設計，無論室外或户外都能帶來全面保護。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294481" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/04_arlopro5-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/04_arlopro5-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/04_arlopro5.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/04_arlopro5-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2>Arlo Essential 2K 室內攝影機（第二代）</h2><p>Arlo Essential 室內攝影機具有私隱保護功能，用户可對鏡頭進行即時遮擋，自由和簡單選擇遮擋和錄影的時間。此外，Arlo Essential 室內攝影機具備 130 度視野、及夜視功能，不分晝夜守護家中環境。加上雙向對話功能，需要時亦能直接透過鏡頭進行通話。</p><p>Arlo 安全攝影機現可透過 Arlo 官網和授權零售商以優惠的新價格購買。如欲瞭解更多資訊，請瀏覽 <a href="https://www.arlo.com/hk/">https://www.arlo.com/hk/</a>。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294482" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/05_arloessential2-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/05_arloessential2-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/05_arloessential2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/27/arlo-price-down/wireless-home/">ARLO 調整家居安全產品價格，震撼降價低至 6 折</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
